data.title: WhoDunnit Hoedown
data.meta_description:
WHODUNNIT HOEDOWN – A “MURDER MYSTERY” DINNER SHOW 

Branson’s Favorite Comedy Murder Mystery Show! The gang is throwing Aunt Bell a surprise birthday party but biggest wing ding in these parts takes a hilariously dark turn. Legendary Fiddler Squeeky Bowman meets his mysterious demise, and the list of suspects is longer than a mules tail! Come have a delicious dinner and lots of laughs, and who knows…you might figure out Who Dun It!

Menu:
BBQ Pulled Pork
& Herb-Roasted Chicken Breast
Mashed Potatoes
Vegetable D’jour
White Birthday Cake
Dinner Roll
Choice of Beverage
